12 O&#039;CLOCK HIGH (1964)

208. Runway in the Dark    11/1/1965  
Gallagher must fly a night mission into Norway to pick up legendary resistance leader Arn Borg who has information on the location of a heavy-water facility.
  Guest star: Robert Dornan (Co-Pilot), Jill Haworth (Fay Vendry) , Peter Bourne (Norwegian Civilian), Donald Ein (Sven), Gil Stuart (British Officer), Pat Cardi (Christian Borg), Albert Paulsen (Arn Borg), Jack Weston (Captain "Chub" Willis), Dinah Ann Rogers (Cynthia Finlay)

209. I Am the Enemy    11/8/1965  (REPOST)
The 918 is on its 8th mission to bomb the sub pens at St Nazaire. This mission is led by Major Kurt Brown (William Shatner) who has never aborted for any reason. The "Iron Major" knows no fear and thinks killing Germans is more important than himself or any of his crew.
  Guest stars:  William Shatner (Major Kurt Brown) Elen Willard (Elizabeth Hoffman) 
Peter Marko (Captain Forbes) Walter Gregg (Lieutenant Daniels)
